    <title>二分</title>
    <url>/2024/03/17/%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95/%E4%BA%8C%E5%88%86/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="二分查找-二分答案"><a href="#二分查找-二分答案" class="headerlink" title="二分查找 &amp; 二分答案"></a>二分查找 &amp; 二分答案</h1><h2 id="二分模板"><a href="#二分模板" class="headerlink" title="二分模板"></a>二分模板</h2><p><strong>模板一(整数二分)</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span> (l &lt; r) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="type">int</span> mid = l + r &gt;&gt; <span class="number">2</span>;  <span class="comment">// ((l + r) / 2)</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="built_in">check</span>(mid)) r = mid;  <span class="comment">// check() 用来判断 mid 是否满足性质</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span> l = mid + <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>模板二(整数二分)</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span>( l &lt; r) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> mid = l + r  + <span class="number">1</span>&gt;&gt; <span class="number">1</span>; <span class="comment">// (l + r + 1) / 2;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="built_in">check</span>(mid)) l = mid;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span> r = mid - <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p><strong>第一个模板是尽量往左找目标，第二个模板是尽量往右找目标。</strong></p>
<p><strong>只要是往左找答案，就用第一个模板，mid 不用加一， r &#x3D; mid , l  加一；</strong></p>
<p><strong>只要是往右找答案，就用第二个模板，mid 需要加一， l &#x3D; mid , r  减一；</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>模板三(浮点二分)</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span>( r - l &gt; <span class="number">1e-5</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">double</span> mid = (l + r) / <span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="built_in">check</span>(mid)) l = mid;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span> r = mid;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p><strong>浮点除法不会取整，所以 mid，l，r，都不用加 1 或减 1.</strong></p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
